OL,3,CDebate to ban Jersey landlords from
OL,4,Cdiscriminating against pet-owners
OL,6,FJersey's States Assembly will debate a
OL,7,Fproposition to ban landlords from
OL,8,Fdiscriminating against tenants who are
OL,9,Fpet owners.
OL,11,FDeputy Catherine Curtis has lodged a
OL,12,Fproposition to prevent landlords from
OL,13,Fimposing 'blanket bans' on keeping
OL,14,Fpets "for no apparent good reason".
OL,16,FShe believes the current system, which
OL,17,Fpermits landlords to refuse potential
OL,18,Ftenants on the basis of their pets,
OL,19,F"causes heartache to families"
OL,20,Funnecessarily.
