OL,3,CDebate to ban Jersey landlords from
OL,4,Cdiscriminating against pet-owners
OL,6,FDeputy Curtis told ITV News that she
OL,7,Fheard cases of "people considering
OL,8,Fleaving the island because properties
OL,9,Fare more expensive over here and it's
OL,10,Fmuch harder to find one that will take
OL,11,Fon pets".
OL,13,FAlternatively, people say they have
OL,14,Fbeen asked to give up their animals by
OL,15,Flandlords, such as Mandy Phillips who
OL,16,Fhas been renting properties in Jersey
OL,17,Ffor 15 years.
OL,19,FAfter adopting her cat - Molly -
OL,20,FMandy's landlord said she must either
OL,21,Fmove or give up the cat.
