OL,3,CDebate to ban Jersey landlords from
OL,4,Cdiscriminating against pet-owners
OL,6,FSince then, Mandy estimates she's had
OL,7,Fto move 18 times, which she says has
OL,8,Fcaused a significant financial burden,
OL,9,Fanxiety, and emotional distress.
OL,11,FMandy explains: "I can see both sides
OL,12,Fto the argument because if it was my
OL,13,Fplace and someone with a pet had
OL,14,Fdestroyed it, I'd be reluctant to rent
OL,15,Fit out to someone with a pet in the
OL,16,Ffuture.
