OL,3,CDebate to ban Jersey landlords from
OL,4,Cdiscriminating against pet-owners
OL,6,F"However, it's really difficult for
OL,7,Fpeople like myself who've got well-
OL,8,Fbehaved dogs, or cats that are
OL,9,Foutdoors most of the time, and are now
OL,10,Fbeing penalised for it."
OL,12,FMandy suggests that instead of blanket
OL,13,Fbans, each tenant's circumstances
OL,14,Fshould be considered on an individual
OL,15,Fbasis, with tenants potentially having
OL,16,Fto pay additional deposits to cover
OL,17,Ftheir pets.
