OL,3,CDebate to ban Jersey landlords from
OL,4,Cdiscriminating against pet-owners
OL,6,FDeputy Curtis' proposition follows
OL,7,Fthis line of thinking, explaining:
OL,8,F"It's perfectly reasonable for a
OL,9,Flandlord to request an extra deposit
OL,10,Fto cover possible extra damage caused
OL,11,Fby pets."
OL,13,FDeputy Max Andrews, who lives in
OL,14,Frented accommodation with his dog
OL,15,FSampson, says he will not be
OL,16,Fsupporting Deputy Curtis' proposals.
OL,18,FHe says the proposition "does not ask
OL,19,Fthe assembly to approve any
OL,20,Flegislation, so it would be very
OL,21,Fdifficult to enforce.
