OL,3,CDebate to ban Jersey landlords from
OL,4,Cdiscriminating against pet-owners
OL,6,FIn a statement, the JLA says: "It
OL,7,Fwould be a lot more helpful if
OL,8,FGovernment were to produce guidance on
OL,9,Fthese issues (especially as to what a
OL,10,F'reasonable reason' for refusing a pet
OL,11,Fis) instead of imposing new laws which
OL,12,Fcould be unnecessarily restrictive."
OL,14,FThe States will debate Deputy Curtis'
OL,15,Fpropositions on Tuesday 12 November.
